  <summary date="2020-12-21T21:40:16Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Modernizing Notice of Lease Terminations for Servicemembers Act of 2020

This bill specifies that a service member who is authorized under current law to terminate a lease of premises or a motor vehicle lease without incurring an early termination fee may use electronic means to provide notice of the termination.</summary>
